        "description": "<p>This plugin shows the status of your Minecraft server using a shortcode and a widget.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Shortcode &#8211; For the shortcode please use [mcserver] or [mcserverplayer]</li>\n<li>Widget &#8211; Set your sidebar widget under dashboard and then design</li>\n</ul>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Download the plugin and unzip it in the &#8220;/wp-content/plugins/&#8221; directory</li>\n<li>Enable the plugin in the adminpanel under &#8220;Plugins&#8221;</li>\n<li>Go to &#8220;MCPing&#8221; and write your server adress and server port</li>\n<li>Use the widget and the shortcode (Widgets can you activate under &#8220;Appearance -&gt; Widgets&#8221;)</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<p>v1.1<br />\n* online players widget and shortcode added<br />\n* german language added<br />\nv1.0<br />\n* plugin was released</p>\n"
